headline: Is Norwegian Cruise Line (NCLH) Pricing Look Attractive After Mixed Multi‑Year Share Performance
summary: If you are wondering whether Norwegian Cruise Line Holdings is attractively priced at today’s level, you are not alone. This article is built to help you unpack that question. The stock last closed at US$22.92, with returns of 10.1% over 7 days, 2.2% over 30 days, 0.6% year to date, a 21.2% decline over 1 year, a 34.0% gain over 3 years, and a 6.1% decline over 5 years.
